des:
It is hard to remember your family's birthdays but with this amazing skill, you can daily check the list of the celebrities having a birthday today. 
It will list out the celebrities having their birthday today. Very useful app for business promoters, social media managers and celebrity fans who never want to forgot to wish them. This amazing celebrity birthday skill will always available for you to tell you celebrities having a birthday today. 
You can also ask for celebrities having a birthday on a particular date. For example, if anytime you want to list out celebrities having a birthday on 27th of May you can find easily with this skill without waiting for 27th May. 
If you want more features or have feedback feel free to reach to us.
You can launch the skill by saying : Alexa, open celebrity birthday
Enjoy the skill.
